Internet Connection Reboot

Written in Kotlin.

Checks the Internet access and restart the computer at the specified time if it fails.

Exemplary startup
java -jar build/libs/InternetConnectionReboot-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar [HOST] [PORT] [SLEEP1] [SLEEP2]

SLEEP1
Internet access check for the first time.

SLEEP2
The second access check after a certain time as the first will fail.
